<paragraph blockId="96.[1436,2643,2972,3478]" lastBlockId="97.[75,1280,291,444]" lastPageId="97" lastPageNumber="697" pageId="96" pageNumber="696">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1438,2138,3449,3478]" pageId="96" pageNumber="696">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
No information 
<subSubSection pageId="97" pageNumber="697" type="conservation">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[75,425,291,325]" pageId="97" pageNumber="697">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Snow Mountains Grassland Mosaic-tailed Rat is probably common and has a large distribution. It is, however, very poorly known.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
